      "content": "wait, r u sure? the scanner flagged it as critical. i don't want to take the risk of a massive data breach if we just keep it running with a waf rule. if we don't do the maintenance now, how certain are we that the endpoint isolation will actually hold? it seems pretty risky to avoid the downtime.",
